0:00:00.000,0:00:02.800
Zita rangu ndi Miss Doris Ugbaji

0:00:02.800,0:00:04.240
Ini ndinobva ku Benue State, Nigeria.

0:00:04.240,0:00:08.260
Ndiri pano kuti ndipupurire kunaka kwa Ishe muhupenyu hwangu.

0:00:08.260,0:00:17.060
Ndakanunurwa pa SCOAN kubva ku mumweya wemukadzi mandiri, 
 kubonyora nekuona zvinonyadzisira.

0:00:17.060,0:00:20.220
Zvose zvakatanga apo ndaive nemakore matanhatu.

0:00:20.220,0:00:26.400
Baba vangu vaiwanzounza vamwe varume mumba medu.

0:00:26.400,0:00:27.440
Vaizonditora.

0:00:27.440,0:00:31.960
Apo ndaida kubvunza kuti, "Baba, handinzwisise. Murume uyu anodei pano? ",

0:00:31.960,0:00:34.940
ivo vaizotaura kuti ndaiva mwana muduku uye ndakanga ndisingazivi zvandakanga ndichiita.

0:00:34.940,0:00:37.740
Ndinofanira kuramba ndakanyarara ndione zvaaizoita.

0:00:37.740,0:00:43.800
Husiku, vaizondibuditsa kunze uye voshandisa huku kuedza kuteketerera imwe mweya mandiri.

0:00:43.800,0:00:48.240
Taizoenda kurwizi, ivo vaizondigeza asi ini handina kunzwisisa kuti sei?

0:00:48.240,0:00:55.100
Pandakanga ndiri muchikoro chepuraimari, ndaive ndakangwara uye ndakachenjera asi handina kumboziva zvaiitika.

0:00:55.100,0:00:59.380
Pandakaenda kuchikoro, vakati vaifanira kundiendesa kune chikoro chebhodhingi.

0:00:59.380,0:01:03.960
Ndakapinda chikoro chebhodhingi, kwandakasangana ne umwe mukadzi.

0:01:03.960,0:01:07.220
Pandakasangana nemukadzi uyu, akati aida kuti ndive shamwari yake.

0:01:07.220,0:01:12.120
Handina kumboziva kuti pane chimwe chinhu chiri pazviri kana kuti aida kundipinza mune chimwe chinhu.

0:01:12.120,0:01:21.220
Pane umwe usiku hunoshamisa, akandidana kuti ndiuye pakona nokuti aive nechimwe chinhu chaaida kundiudza.

0:01:21.220,0:01:22.720
Ndakati, "Zvakanaka, regai tiende".

0:01:22.720,0:01:27.560
Pakati peusiku, akandimutsa ndokutanga kundibata.

0:01:27.560,0:01:31.200
Chimwe chinhu chakauya pamusoro pangu uye ndizvo zvakaitika kuti ndisumwe kune mweya wemukadzi.

0:01:31.200,0:01:33.760
Ndakatanga kuva nerudo kuvakadzi.

0:01:33.760,0:01:36.120
Aizondibata; Ndaizomubata.

0:01:36.120,0:01:38.420
Zuva rakatevera, ndakadzoka zvakare.

0:01:38.420,0:01:41.620
Takatanga kuzviita.

0:01:41.620,0:01:45.560
Pose paaindiona nemumwe mukadzi, aizotanga kundirwisa,

0:01:45.560,0:01:48.940
achindibvunza kuti sei ndaifamba nemukadzi iyeye uye kuti chii chaive chichiitika.

0:01:48.940,0:01:51.740
Ndakatanga kuva nerudo kuvakadzi.

0:01:51.740,0:01:57.120
Zvakakanganisa hupenyu hwangu nenzira dzakawanda zvokuti kunyange mukirasi, handina kukwanisa kuisa pfungwa pamwe chete.

0:01:57.120,0:02:00.240
Chaizoitika ndechekuti aizouya kunze kwehwindo nokundipa chiratidzo.

0:02:00.240,0:02:02.520
Taizoenda ku dhomitari.

0:02:02.520,0:02:07.220
Ndaizotaura kuti ndakanga ndisinganzwe zvakanaka kana kutsvaga chero chikonzero chekuti ndiende ku dhomitari

0:02:07.220,0:02:10.740
kuti ini naye tive nenguva yakanaka.

0:02:10.740,0:02:15.500
Kubva ipapo, ndakatanga kufambidzana nevasikana vakawanda; Ndakatanga kudanana nevakadzi.

0:02:15.500,0:02:20.700
Kwese kwandaienda, kana ndikavaona, ndaiziva kuti uyu aiva mhando yemweya wacho; isu taizivana pachedu.

0:02:20.700,0:02:22.220
Hataifanira kubvunza.

0:02:22.220,0:02:26.500
Dzimwe nguva, ndaizobvunzwa kuti sei ndaifamba nemusikana uye kana pane chimwe chinhu chatakanga tichiita.

0:02:26.500,0:02:30.900
Ndaizoti kwete uye Mwari achirambidza asi dzaiva nhema; mandiri, ndaiziva zvandakanga ndichiita.

0:02:30.900,0:02:34.540
Pandakadzoka kumusha, ndainyepedzera kuitira kuti amai vangu varege kuziva zvaiitika.

0:02:34.540,0:02:36.440
Zvaizoitika ndezvekuti, ndainge ndiri mukamuri yangu.

0:02:36.440,0:02:43.660
Pose pandairota nezve mukadzi achiuya kwandiri uye achiita bonde kwandiri, ndaizotanga kubonyora.

0:02:43.660,0:02:44.600
Zvakanaka

0:02:44.600,0:02:49.280
Saka, iwe unoreva kuti, kunze kwekusangana panyama ne musikana iyeye kuchikoro,

0:02:49.280,0:02:53.080
uyo akakusuma kune muitiro uyu wemweya wemukadzi,

0:02:53.080,0:02:55.800
waivewo nehope dzomukadzi aiuya kwauri.

0:02:55.800,0:02:57.560
Ungatiudze here zvimwe pamusoro paizvozvo?

0:02:57.560,0:02:59.320
Hungu, ndaiwanzo rota.

0:02:59.320,0:03:04.480
Umwe mukadzi aizouya kwandiri muchiroto uye chero nguva iyo mukadzi uyu aiuya kwandiri -

0:03:04.480,0:03:08.960
Kana ndisina kuona chero mukadzi padyo neni kuti ndiite izvozvo naye, ndaitanga kubonyora.

0:03:08.960,0:03:12.500
Ndaikwanisa kubonyora mukamuri yangu kwemazuva maviri kusvika matatu; Ndaisazobuda.

0:03:12.500,0:03:15.020
Handaidya asi ndaizogutsikana.

0:03:15.020,0:03:20.320
Munhu wose aizouya kuzogogodza pamukova wangu, ndaizova nehasha dzaigona kuuraya munhu.

0:03:20.320,0:03:22.560
Ndaizorwa ndichiti hakuna munhu anofanira kuuya pagonhi rangu.

0:03:22.560,0:03:24.880
Hapana aiziva zvandaita mukamuri yangu.

0:03:24.880,0:03:29.380
Ndakanga ndiri munyika yangu ndega; Ndakanga ndisingadi kuti munhu andiraire.

0:03:29.380,0:03:36.500
Mweya uyu wakandisundira kuti ndinwe uye hakuna munhu aiziva kuti ndakanga ndiri munhu ainwa.

0:03:36.500,0:03:42.760
Nemhaka yekutarisika kwangu, hawaimboziva kunze kwekuti iwe wakandibata ndichiita chimwe chinhu kana chimwe.

0:03:42.760,0:03:44.680
Ndakatanga kuparapatika kuchikoro.

0:03:44.680,0:03:57.620
Ndisati ndapedza chikoro changu chesekondari, ndakanyora mazamanisheni kanokwana kana.

0:03:57.620,0:04:00.580
Hapana aifunga kuti ndaizoenda kuchikoro chepamusoro nokuti

0:04:00.580,0:04:03.360
rudzi rwehupenyu hwandakanga ndichirarama hwakanga hune ngozi.

0:04:03.360,0:04:06.800
Saka iwe uri mumwe munhu aive akangwara izvi zvisati zvaitika, ndizvo?

0:04:06.800,0:04:08.600
Hongu.

0:04:08.600,0:04:14.020
Asi mushure mekunge izvi zvaitika, mamakisi ako ose, kuverenga kwako - iwe wakangobvisa pfungwa iyoyo mumusoro mako, handiti?

0:04:14.020,0:04:15.940
Hungu, ndakanga ndisingakwanisi kuita chero chinhu kuchikoro.

0:04:15.940,0:04:19.740
Panzvimbo yekuti ndiite zvechikoro, ndaizenge ndichitarisa vakadzi vekuti ndisangane navo.

0:04:19.740,0:04:24.840
Kwese kwandaisangana navo, ini ndaizove murume; ivo vaizova mukadzi.

0:04:24.840,0:04:36.160
Pandakakwanisa kuenda kuchikoro chepamusoro, zvinhu zvakawanda zvakaitika kwandiri asi ndakakwanisa kupedza.

0:04:36.160,0:04:39.980
Mweya uyu wemudzimai wakakanganisa sei ukama hwako nevanhurume,

0:04:39.980,0:04:45.620
zvichida vakomana vaifarira kuva neukama newe?

0:04:45.620,0:04:52.760
Mweya uyu wakandibata zvikuru zvokuti ndaivenga varume; pose pandaiona varume, vainditsamwisa.

0:04:52.760,0:04:56.040
Ndaivenga vanhurume; Ndakanga ndisingafariri kuva pedyo nevarume.

0:04:56.040,0:05:00.320
Apo mumwe munhu akauya kuzotaura kuti aida kuve shamwari yangu, ndaiti zvakanaka

0:05:00.320,0:05:05.200
asi pavaizotora nguva yavo, ndaivavenga.

0:05:05.200,0:05:09.300
Ndakanga ndisina rudo kuvanhurume; Ndakanga ndiine rudo kuvanhukadzi chete.

0:05:09.300,0:05:14.080
Kunyangwe dai ndakanga ndisingaiti chero chinhu nemukadzi, ndaisarudza kuva nevakadzi.

0:05:14.080,0:05:14.720
Zvakanaka.

0:05:14.720,0:05:19.100
Izvi zvakakanganisa sei ukama hwako nemhuri yako?

0:05:19.100,0:05:24.300
Zvaka kanganisa ukama hwangu nemhuri yangu pakuti pakanga pasina rugare.

0:05:24.300,0:05:25.760
Mai vangu, ndaivavenga-

0:05:25.760,0:05:28.180
Apo umwe munhu aitaura neni-

0:05:28.180,0:05:32.740
Ndaizoudza baba vangu kuti kana vasina kundipa mari, ndaizodana mbavha dzine zvombo kuti dziuye,

0:05:32.740,0:05:34.280
kuzoitora kubva kwavari vachizoipa kwandiri.

0:05:34.280,0:05:37.860
Ndakarwisa munhu wose.

0:05:37.860,0:05:44.860
Ndakatenga mapanga maviri kuitira kuti parege kuva nomunhu aizotaura neni nokuti ndaizomubaya.

0:05:44.860,0:05:49.160
Havai kwanisa kutaura neni; kwakanga kusina rugare - munhu wose aindivenga.

0:05:49.160,0:05:52.780
Mai vangu vakatanga kutaura kuti ini ndakange ndisiri mwanasikana wavakabereka;

0:05:52.780,0:05:55.220
chimwe chinhu chakanga chisina kunaka uye zvakanga zvisiri zvega

0:05:55.220,0:05:59.900
Vakandiudza kuti ndiende ku SCOAN; vanhu vaienda ikoko uye iniwo ndinofanirawo.

0:05:59.900,0:06:02.900
Ndakati handidi kuuya nokuti ndaiziva kuti mweya wangu waizoratidzwa pachena

0:06:02.900,0:06:05.260
sezvo ndaiziva kuti paive ne mweya wakandikomberedza.

0:06:05.260,0:06:08.240
Waiziva kubvira panguva iyoyo kuti iri raiva dambudziko remweya?

0:06:08.240,0:06:09.040
Hongu.

0:06:09.040,0:06:09.580
Zvakanaka

0:06:09.580,0:06:13.760
Pawakasvika pano, munguva yemunyengetero weruzhinji, tiudze kuti chii chakaitika.

0:06:13.760,0:06:15.240
Panguva yemunyengetero we ruzhinji, ndaive uko.

0:06:15.240,0:06:19.720
Munamato usati waitika, ndakasangana newechidiki ndikamuudza kuti handinzwisise upenyu hwangu,

0:06:19.720,0:06:26.420
Ndakanga ndichitarisana nematambudziko akawanda uye ndakanga ndisingazivi kwandiri kuenda kana kuti ndiri kuenda mberi here kana shure

0:06:26.420,0:06:31.720
Munhu wacho akati ndinofanira kuenda kumunyengetero we ruzhinji.

0:06:31.720,0:06:34.460
Mupfungwa dzangu ndakati, "Munamato we ruzhinji rudzii?"

0:06:34.460,0:06:36.300
Ndaida kutiza.

0:06:36.300,0:06:41.560
Pandakanga ndichiedza kuenda, makumbo angu akatanga kurema uye handina kukwanisa kuenda.

0:06:41.560,0:06:46.940
Ndakangokwanisa kugara mune imwe kona pavakatanga munyengetero we ruzhinji.

0:06:46.940,0:06:50.680
Ikoko ndiko kwandakasunungurwa kubva mumweya uyu.

0:06:50.680,0:06:55.420
Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe chete kuna Jesu!

0:06:55.420,0:07:00.100
Tine vanhu vazhinji muchechi ino nhasi vasina kumbobvira vanzwa munyengetero weruzhinji kare.

0:07:00.100,0:07:03.960
Tinoda kuti utiudze; apo munyengetero waienderera mberi, chii chakaitika,

0:07:03.960,0:07:07.820
chii chaive chichinyatsoitika kwauri? Rondedzera izvozvi kwatiri.

0:07:07.820,0:07:12.080
Pandakanga ndava kuda kuenda, muviri wangu wose wakapisa.

0:07:12.080,0:07:16.220
Handizivi kuti dikita rakawandisa raibuda mumuviri wangu rakabva kupi.

0:07:16.220,0:07:19.000
Ndakakwanisa kugara pasi pavainge vachinyengetera.

0:07:19.000,0:07:23.060
Zvadaro, ndakanzwa ruzha sekunge vairidza ngoma munzeve dzangu.

0:07:23.060,0:07:30.980
Ndakanga ndichitsvaga nzira yekubuda nayo; Ndakatanga kuona rima uye ndakanzwa kupisa kumativi ose emuviri wangu.

0:07:30.980,0:07:36.820
Ndakatanga kurutsa uye kubva ipapo, ndakawira pasi; Ndakanga ndisisazivi zvandakanga ndichiita.

0:07:36.820,0:07:43.740
Mushure mekurutsa, tirikuona pasikirini izvozvi, nguva iyo mweya wakaipa wairatidzira mauri.

0:07:43.740,0:07:46.440
Unoyeuka here chimwe cheizvi?

0:07:46.440,0:07:47.680
Kwete.

0:07:47.680,0:07:48.600
Iwe haurangariri izvozvo?

0:07:48.600,0:07:49.640
Aiwa.

0:07:49.640,0:07:54.880
Rumbidzai Mwari! Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe chete kuna Jesu!

0:07:54.880,0:07:57.700
Zvechokwadi, uko kwaiva kudzikinurwa musimba re Mweya Mutsvene.

0:07:57.700,0:08:03.960
Mushure mechiitiko ichocho, pawakanunurwa, tiudze; Ndekupi kuchinja kwawakaona?

0:08:03.960,0:08:11.000
Zvakandishamisa ini, ndakaona kuti mushure mekudzikinurwa, foni yangu iyo yakanga yakaita sezvokudya kwandiri

0:08:11.000,0:08:18.280
sezvo ndaigara ndichiona zvinhu zvakasiyana pairi, ndaisazovata asi zvino, ini handishandisi foni yangu.

0:08:18.280,0:08:21.520
Ndinonzwa sekurangwa kuenda pa Indaneti.

0:08:21.520,0:08:30.480
Ndakatanga kufunga zvakanaka kuti mukadzi anofanira kuroorwa uye ave nevana vake.

0:08:30.480,0:08:33.120
Handina kumbofunga kuti pane chimwe chinhu chakadai.

0:08:33.120,0:08:35.960
Amai vangu vaizondibvunza, "Iwe hausi kuda kuroorwa; varume vari kuuya? "

0:08:35.960,0:08:38.360
Ndaifunga kuti, "Mukadzi mukuru uyu haazive zviri kuitika".

0:08:38.360,0:08:43.220
Handai taura navo kwevhiki; Ini ndaizonyangarika kubva mumba ndoenda kundosangana nevanasikana vangu.

0:08:43.220,0:08:46.680
Kubvira ipapo, rudo rwevakadzi rwakapera?

0:08:46.680,0:08:48.580
Hongu, zvose zvakamira.

0:08:48.580,0:08:58.040
Ndinoona vakadzi sana sisi vangu; Handivaoni ndofunga zvekufambidzana zvakare.

0:08:58.040,0:09:02.620
Zvakadini nehope dzawaimbova nadzo dzemukadzi aiuya kwauri usiku kuti akutambudze?

0:09:02.620,0:09:08.520
Hungu, ndaigara ndichirota ndichidya uye vakadzi vakasiyana vachiuya kuzoita bonde neni.

0:09:08.520,0:09:10.620
Handichazvionazve.

0:09:10.620,0:09:14.620
Chiroto icho ndakave nacho ndechanezuro husiku, ndakakwira ndege ndichibva kwandaive ndichienda ku SCOAN.

0:09:14.620,0:09:18.720
Ndakaenda ku SCOAN ndikamhara. Ndizvo zvose.

0:09:18.720,0:09:24.420
Hareruya, ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe chete kuna Jesu, Mambo we Kubwinya!

0:09:24.420,0:09:30.080
Nedzikinuro iyi yawakawana, tinoda kuti iwe upe mazano kuvatarisi vari kukuona pasi rose,

0:09:30.080,0:09:31.940
pamwe nesu, tirikuteerera muchechi ino.

0:09:31.940,0:09:34.220
Inzwi rako re yambiro nderipi?

0:09:34.220,0:09:39.620
Zano rangu kune vanoona kunze uko, kunyanya madzimai vechidiki  vaduku vakaita seni.

0:09:39.620,0:09:42.220
Ndinoziva kuti pane vanhu vakawanda kunze uko vari kundiona.

0:09:42.220,0:09:48.440
Hapana chero chinhu chino ndinyadzisa; Ndiri kufara chaizvo kumira pamberi pa Mwari nekupa uchapupu uhwu.

0:09:48.440,0:09:51.140
Hapana chinhu icho Mwari asingagoni kukuitira.

0:09:51.140,0:09:56.480
Mwari mumwechete akandinunura achanunura avo vane dambudziko serangu.

0:09:56.480,0:10:02.820
Variko vakawanda kunze uko; Ndinoziva kuti vangani vandakange ndichitevera.

0:10:02.820,0:10:09.480
Ndapota, gadzirira kusunungurwa kwako uuye ku SCOAN

0:10:09.480,0:10:12.400
nokuti ndipo pandakawana ruponeso rwangu.

0:10:12.400,0:10:13.260
Hareruya!

0:10:13.260,0:10:16.460
Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe chete kuna Jesu!

0:10:16.460,0:10:21.720
Iwawo mazano akanaka; kana tine dambudziko, tinofanira kumhanyira kuna Ishe ne Muponesi wedu Jesu Kristu,

0:10:21.720,0:10:26.160
isu tinofanira kumhanyira kune chechi ine mweya mupenyu, iyo SCOAN inongova imwe yadzo.

0:10:26.160,0:10:31.600
Tinotenda kuti apo iwe unoramba uchiita kuti Shoko ra Mwari rive nhungamiro ye hupenyu hwako; zviri nani hazvina kukwana -

0:10:31.600,0:10:35.860
zvakanakisisa zvichiri kuuya kwauri nemhuri yako, muzita ra Jesu!

0:10:35.860,0:10:37.920
Ameni.

